{"id":"be-pronouns","track":"foundation","order":3,"title":{"en":"Pronouns, determiners & joiners","zh":"代词、限定词、连接词"},"trick":{"heading":{"en":"Pronouns, determiners & joiners","zh":"代词、限定词与连接词"},"body":{"en":"A small set carries grammar: pronouns (I, he, you, who), determiners (a, the, some, any, no, this, that, every), and joiners (and, but, or, if). Questions use who/what/how/when/where/why. These few words connect everything else.","zh":"少数词承载语法：代词（I, he, you, who）、限定词（a, the, some, any, no, this, that, every）、连接词（and, but, or, if）。疑问用 who/what/how/when/where/why。这些词把其余一切连接起来。"},"examples":[{"text":"some water","note":{"en":"some = uncountable amount","zh":"some=不可数的量"}},{"text":"the dog and the cat","note":{"en":"and joins","zh":"and 连接"}}]},"words":[{"w":"a","pos":"det","cefr":"A1","gloss":{"en":"used before a noun for one thing not yet known","zh":"一个（不定冠词）"},"example":"I have a dog.","blank":"a"},{"w":"the","pos":"det","cefr":"A1","gloss":{"en":"used before a known or already-mentioned thing","zh":"这个；那个（定冠词）"},"example":"The dog is big.","blank":"The"},{"w":"all","pos":"det","cefr":"A2","gloss":{"en":"the whole number or amount of something","zh":"全部；所有"},"example":"All the children are here.","blank":"All"},{"w":"any","pos":"det","cefr":"A2","gloss":{"en":"some, in questions or negatives","zh":"任何；一些"},"example":"Do you have any water?","blank":"any"},{"w":"every","pos":"det","cefr":"A1","gloss":{"en":"each one of a group","zh":"每一个"},"example":"She knows every student in the school.","blank":"every"},{"w":"no","pos":"det","cefr":"A1","gloss":{"en":"not one; not any","zh":"没有；无"},"example":"There is no milk in the cup.","blank":"no"},{"w":"other","pos":"det","cefr":"A1","gloss":{"en":"different from the one already named","zh":"其他的；另外的"},"example":"I will read the other book.","blank":"other"},{"w":"some","pos":"det","cefr":"A1","gloss":{"en":"an amount or number that is not given","zh":"一些；若干"},"example":"There's some milk in the fridge.","blank":"some"},{"w":"such","pos":"det","cefr":"A2","gloss":{"en":"of this or that kind; to a high degree","zh":"这样的；如此的"},"example":"It was such a good day.","blank":"such"},{"w":"that","pos":"det","cefr":"B2","gloss":{"en":"the one over there or already named","zh":"那个"},"example":"I like that house.","blank":"that"},{"w":"this","pos":"det","cefr":"B1","gloss":{"en":"the one here or near you","zh":"这个"},"example":"This book is mine.","blank":"This"},{"w":"i","pos":"pron","cefr":"A1","gloss":{"en":"the person who is speaking","zh":"我"},"example":"I am happy today.","blank":"I"},{"w":"he","pos":"pron","cefr":"A1","gloss":{"en":"a male person already named","zh":"他"},"example":"He is my father.","blank":"He"},{"w":"you","pos":"pron","cefr":"A1","gloss":{"en":"the person or people I am talking to","zh":"你；你们"},"example":"You said you knew the way.","blank":"You"},{"w":"who","pos":"pron","cefr":"A1","gloss":{"en":"used to ask about which person","zh":"谁"},"example":"Who is that woman?","blank":"Who"},{"w":"and","pos":"conj","cefr":"A1","gloss":{"en":"used to join words or ideas","zh":"和；并且"},"example":"I have bread and butter.","blank":"and"},{"w":"because","pos":"conj","cefr":"A1","gloss":{"en":"for the reason that","zh":"因为"},"example":"I did it because he told me to.","blank":"because"},{"w":"but","pos":"conj","cefr":"B2","gloss":{"en":"used to show a different or opposite idea","zh":"但是"},"example":"I am small but strong.","blank":"but"},{"w":"or","pos":"conj","cefr":"A1","gloss":{"en":"used to show another choice","zh":"或者"},"example":"Do you want tea or water?","blank":"or"},{"w":"if","pos":"conj","cefr":"A1","gloss":{"en":"used to say one thing depends on another","zh":"如果"},"example":"If you see him, give him this note.","blank":"If"},{"w":"though","pos":"conj","cefr":"B2","gloss":{"en":"used to add a fact that softens what was said","zh":"虽然；不过"},"example":"Our team lost. It was a good game though.","blank":"though"},{"w":"while","pos":"conj","cefr":"B1","gloss":{"en":"during the time that something happens","zh":"当……的时候"},"example":"He called while I was asleep.","blank":"while"},{"w":"how","pos":"adv","cefr":"A1","gloss":{"en":"in what way","zh":"怎样；如何"},"example":"How does it work?","blank":"How"},{"w":"when","pos":"adv","cefr":"A1","gloss":{"en":"at what time","zh":"什么时候"},"example":"When did you last see him?","blank":"When"},{"w":"where","pos":"adv","cefr":"A1","gloss":{"en":"in or to what place","zh":"在哪里；到哪里"},"example":"Where do you live?","blank":"Where"},{"w":"why","pos":"adv","cefr":"A1","gloss":{"en":"for what reason","zh":"为什么"},"example":"Why were you late?","blank":"Why"},{"w":"again","pos":"adv","cefr":"A1","gloss":{"en":"one more time","zh":"再一次；又"},"example":"Please say it again.","blank":"again"},{"w":"ever","pos":"adv","cefr":"A2","gloss":{"en":"at any time","zh":"曾经；从来"},"example":"Have you ever been here?","blank":"ever"},{"w":"far","pos":"adv","cefr":"B2","gloss":{"en":"a long way away","zh":"远；遥远"},"example":"The shop is not far from here.","blank":"far"},{"w":"forward","pos":"adv","cefr":"B2","gloss":{"en":"towards the front","zh":"向前"},"example":"He took one step forward.","blank":"forward"},{"w":"here","pos":"adv","cefr":"A1","gloss":{"en":"in or to this place","zh":"这里"},"example":"I live here.","blank":"here"},{"w":"near","pos":"adv","cefr":"B1","gloss":{"en":"a short distance away","zh":"近；附近"},"example":"His house is very near.","blank":"near"},{"w":"now","pos":"adv","cefr":"B1","gloss":{"en":"at this time","zh":"现在"},"example":"Where are you living now?","blank":"now"},{"w":"out","pos":"adv","cefr":"A1","gloss":{"en":"away from the inside","zh":"出去；在外"},"example":"She ran out into the corridor.","blank":"out"},{"w":"still","pos":"adv","cefr":"B1","gloss":{"en":"up to now and not stopping","zh":"仍然；还"},"example":"He is still at work.","blank":"still"},{"w":"then","pos":"adv","cefr":"A1","gloss":{"en":"at that time; next","zh":"那时；然后"},"example":"We ate, then we slept.","blank":"then"},{"w":"there","pos":"adv","cefr":"A1","gloss":{"en":"in or to that place","zh":"那里"},"example":"Put the box over there.","blank":"there"},{"w":"together","pos":"adv","cefr":"A1","gloss":{"en":"with each other","zh":"一起"},"example":"We grew up together.","blank":"together"},{"w":"well","pos":"adv","cefr":"C1","gloss":{"en":"in a good way","zh":"好；很好地"},"example":"She sings very well.","blank":"well"},{"w":"almost","pos":"adv","cefr":"A2","gloss":{"en":"very nearly but not quite","zh":"几乎；差不多"},"example":"I like almost all of them.","blank":"almost"},{"w":"enough","pos":"adv","cefr":"A2","gloss":{"en":"as much as is needed","zh":"足够地"},"example":"This box is big enough.","blank":"enough"},{"w":"even","pos":"adv","cefr":"B2","gloss":{"en":"used to show something is surprising","zh":"甚至"},"example":"He runs fast, even in the rain.","blank":"even"},{"w":"little","pos":"adv","cefr":"A2","gloss":{"en":"to a small degree; not much","zh":"很少；不多"},"example":"She ate a little before work.","blank":"little"},{"w":"much","pos":"adv","cefr":"A1","gloss":{"en":"to a great degree","zh":"很；非常"},"example":"Thank you very much.","blank":"much"},{"w":"not","pos":"adv","cefr":"A1","gloss":{"en":"used to make a word or idea negative","zh":"不；没有"},"example":"I am not tired.","blank":"not"},{"w":"only","pos":"adv","cefr":"A1","gloss":{"en":"and no one or nothing else","zh":"只；仅仅"},"example":"I have only one apple.","blank":"only"},{"w":"quite","pos":"adv","cefr":"A2","gloss":{"en":"to some degree; fairly","zh":"相当；颇"},"example":"The film was quite good.","blank":"quite"},{"w":"so","pos":"adv","cefr":"A2","gloss":{"en":"to such a great degree","zh":"如此；这么"},"example":"Don't look so angry.","blank":"so"},{"w":"very","pos":"adv","cefr":"B2","gloss":{"en":"to a high degree","zh":"很；非常"},"example":"She is very kind.","blank":"very"},{"w":"tomorrow","pos":"adv","cefr":"A1","gloss":{"en":"on the day after today","zh":"明天"},"example":"See you tomorrow.","blank":"tomorrow"},{"w":"yesterday","pos":"adv","cefr":"A1","gloss":{"en":"on the day before today","zh":"昨天"},"example":"I saw him yesterday.","blank":"yesterday"},{"w":"north","pos":"adv","cefr":"A2","gloss":{"en":"in or towards the north","zh":"在北方；向北"},"example":"The birds fly north in spring.","blank":"north"},{"w":"south","pos":"adv","cefr":"A2","gloss":{"en":"in or towards the south","zh":"在南方；向南"},"example":"We drove south for an hour.","blank":"south"},{"w":"east","pos":"adv","cefr":"A2","gloss":{"en":"in or towards the east","zh":"在东方；向东"},"example":"The sun comes up in the east.","blank":"east"},{"w":"west","pos":"adv","cefr":"A2","gloss":{"en":"in or towards the west","zh":"在西方；向西"},"example":"The sun goes down in the west.","blank":"west"},{"w":"please","pos":"adv","cefr":"A2","gloss":{"en":"a polite word when asking for something","zh":"请"},"example":"Please sit down.","blank":"Please"},{"w":"yes","pos":"adv","cefr":"A1","gloss":{"en":"used to say something is true or right","zh":"是；对"},"example":"Yes, this is my car.","blank":"Yes"}]}